node.text:
— Whew, chile! I just learned so much about vaginal health from this @thedoseshow interview with @marriedtomedicine star @therealdrjackie. She spoke about what to do AND not to do to maintain a healthy & balanced Queen V 👑

This interview was one of my favorites for so many reasons! Dr. Jackie is not only an award winning OBGYN, author, reality tv star and entrepreneur — but she is an idol of mine simply because she is the definition of YOU CAN DO BOTH. Everyone knows how much I advocate for true renaissance women in medicine. Tune in NOW to watch the episode in my bio 🎥

One question for the ladies, how do you care for down there? 🌸🤔

#drrobinb #drjackie #marriedtomedicine #womeninmedicine #womenempowerment #prettylittledoctor #obgyn #gyno #thedoseshow #pharmacy #blackfemaledoctors #realitytv #vaginalhealth

— Always up for a challenge 🔝 @1stphorm 

Good health to me is holistic. It’s starts from the inside out. It’s from what you eat to the way you dress. That’s why I challenge myself mentally and physically to take everything I do to the next level. 

#IAM1STPHORM #drrobinb #fitdoc #versatility

node.text:
— Something’s coming & I’ve been anticipating this drop for a while. Most of you are new to my platform, but one thing that’s near & dear to my heart is my business baby @muze.labs 🖤

I launched this skin care brand with everything I had in me while IN pharmacy school and during a pandemic. Invested pretty much all I had, built the website myself when developers fell through, had an investor but decided to do it alone, had mentorship but no employees. The list goes on. 

BUT I did it because I wanted to create clean beauty products that I wish existed as a pharmacist. I travel, train, and I’m always on the go. I needed skin care that can keep up with my busy lifestyle! And I know a lot of you can relate.

Moral of the story? Keep following your dreams, no matter how challenging. Just make sure you come back and better. AND you can’t do it alone. Thank you to everyone that helped me with the relaunch. You are so appreciated. ✨
